	pico far east holdings ltd
	
Pico Far East Holdings Limited Recommends Interim Dividend for the Six Months Ended April 30, 2017, Payable on July 28, 2017
Jun 27 17
The Board of Pico Far East Holdings Limited recommended the payment of an interim dividend of HK 4.5 cents per share for the six months ended April 30, 2017 against HK 4.5 cents paid a year ago. The interim dividend will be payable on July 28, 2017 to shareholders on the register of members of the company on July 21, 2017.


Pico Far East Holdings Ltd. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Six Months Ended April 30, 2017
Jun 27 17
Pico Far East Holdings Ltd. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the six months ended April 30, 2017. For the period, the company reported turnover of HKD 1,710,063,000 compared with HKD 2,024,872,000 for the same period last year. Profit from operations was HKD 144,245,000 compared with HKD 158,927,000 for the same period last year. Profit before tax was HKD 157,048,000 compared with HKD 173,018,000 for the same period last year. Profit for the period attributable to owners of the company was HKD 123,744,000 or 10.08 cents diluted per share compared with HKD 128,723,000 or 10.53 cents diluted per share for the same period last year. Net cash generated from operating activities was HKD 200,489,000 compared with HKD 106,574,000 for the same period last year.


Pico Far East Holdings Limited to Report First Half, 2017 Results on Jun 27, 2017
Jun 15 17
Pico Far East Holdings Limited announced that they will report first half, 2017 results on Jun 27, 2017








 












