Pico Far East Holdings Ltd

- Hong Kong
				
				






























									
																			
						Pico is a global group of agencies specialising in engaging people, creating experiences and activating brands. Our strength comes from the diversity of over 2,000 inspired professionals in over 40 major cities worldwide. Backed by some 70,000 sq. m. of production facilities across five continents, we are passionate about achieving our clients’ missions across multiple activation platforms –from exhibitionsand events, retail, themed environments, visual identity, sports marketing and overlays, and venue management and consultation; to content, sponsorship activation, below-the-line and above-the-line engagement marketing, and digital and technology solutions.
					
				





